OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Ffine and dry this evening with plenty
OL,7,Fof late sunshine. Little change
OL,8,Fovernight with largely clear skies.
OL,9,FRisk of some lower cloud pushing into
OL,10,Fthe east of the country. A warm night,
OL,11,Fespecially in the towns and cities.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FAnother dry and sunny day
OL,14,Fonce any early morning low cloud and
OL,15,Fmist clears. Feeling very warm,
OL,16,Fespecially in the strong sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
