OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FRemaining largely dry and settled
OL,7,Fthroughout. A small chance of a few
OL,8,Fshowers Thursday, but most will avoid
OL,9,Fthem. Very warm initially but a little
OL,10,Fless warm by Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
